{"tid":385407,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[DSE maths] 再分享多個做mc 既技巧","createTime":"2017-09-03T08:00:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-07T01:32:14.000Z","uid":126679,"like":2,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"70839cd34ba24110db128d4d83e3728358239ff2","tid":385407,"uid":126679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T08:00:10.000Z","msg":"上一集講左2017 年Q41<br />\n一條大家都覺得好難既題目<br />\n<br />\n今集第七集就講一條好似好易<br />\n但年報話得好少人啱既題目<br />\n有關於change of subject<br />\n片段在此<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8TWMGwLmCrI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8TWMGwLmCrI&d=bPK0oh70e0%2B6TKpohi9AyUzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=6a49bdb4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8TWMGwLmCrI</a><br />\n<br />\n如有興趣既可以睇埋其他幾集<br />\n希望幫到你係MC上拎高d分啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外我都有一個fb page<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/dsechemathsbob/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdsechemathsbob%2F&d=bPK0oh70e0%2B6TKpohi9AyUzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=67fc924f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/dsechemathsbob/</a><br />\n如有任何問題, 歡迎inbox我<br />\n包括maths core , M1 , M2 或者chemistry既問題<br />\n唔想inbox既同學都可以tg我<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/gggary\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fgggary&d=bPK0oh70e0%2B6TKpohi9AyUzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=69609194\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/gggary</a><br />\n以上條link都一樣搵到我既<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">以下係個小小的廣告<br />\n因為都有唔少同學仔tg我問有關補習既問題<br />\n我想係呢度簡單講少少<br />\n暫時我係開左math 同 chem 既course <br />\n<br />\nMaths:<br />\n1. MC super skills <br />\nyoutube片段入面只係全course 既極少部分, 仲有唔同題形既變化, 再加埋好多低於40%命中率既問題既技巧都會教<br />\n我全部既示範都係base on 考試局 past paper<br />\n絕對唔係 只係用到一次既&quot;懶係野&quot;技巧<br />\n<br />\nChem:<br />\n1. Intensive course<br />\n幾個月從頭學過DSE chem 佔分最重既topic eg: redox, organic chem, 計數 等等, 仲會包埋2個electives, 當中會包曬你一定要識既concepts, 練習, past paper <br />\n簡單d講就係你肯比心機, 一定追得到<br />\n<br />\n以上課程應該只適合F.6 或者 重讀生<br />\n因為我每一句上堂對白都係圍繞考試<br />\n加上因為中午時間會多d課室<br />\n所以重讀生會好d<br />\n地點方面會港島區有一個, 九龍區都有一個<br />\n<br />\n如同學有興趣<br />\n詳細價錢地點或者其他問題可以fb inbox 我或者tg我<br />\n廢事比人話sell</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再次祝各位<br />\n開學充實<br />\n溫書溫得超級入腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c18a9df8895128273e7eee9c95c152bad46cdb7","tid":385407,"uid":126679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T10:20:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d96ccff78f18fcdef86a32107d6265a61d39595","tid":385407,"uid":12754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T19:07:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d4cfbb02485feaa5101b712631a373c8a803a91","tid":385407,"uid":126679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T17:54:53.000Z","msg":"多左人問math mc course 既內容<br />\n到底有咩題形？<br />\n會教d咩技巧<br />\n我簡單講幾句<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/06/013706_e66a7aa1f9e654f659925df2363b14bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F06%2F013706_e66a7aa1f9e654f659925df2363b14bd.jpg&h=c9917a5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上圖係一大本筆記既部分題目<br />\n首先正如我所講，全部出自past paper<br />\n你可以見到當年答啱既percentage<br />\n簡單d講<br />\n我係教你<span style=\"color: red;\">如何揀到正確答案</span><br />\n亦可以話呢個course <span style=\"color: red;\">不是教你計啱條數</span><br />\n<br />\n呢個course創立既目的其實得一個<br />\n我就係希望用最短既時間<br />\n令你答啱更多難既題目<br />\n幫你升多個grade<br />\n我唔想數學成為大家入大學展翅高飛既<span style=\"color: red;\">絆腳石</span><br />\n相反，數學可能係你入大學既<span style=\"color: red;\">踏腳石</span><br />\n<br />\n我而家想做既野<br />\n就好似我個名咁<br />\n能夠幫到你入讀你心儀學系，唔使比dse封鎖你既未來係我點解又開page又開tg答問題既原因<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n我只係想講<br />\n印大本notes, exercises, book 場係要好多成本<br />\n而我收既價錢真係極平"},{"pid":"be40613573b40bbbce4639e5262259d167921fee","tid":385407,"uid":137669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T18:17:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07fcfb68f97e1ac3863f8f28c3effd354aa1b3af","tid":385407,"uid":126679,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T02:02:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"503414a5311715d40dc1f3e4043fe3fe3c049f6d","tid":385407,"uid":126679,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T01:32:14.000Z","msg":"math mc 快滿<br />\n一夠人就馬上開始了<br />\n早d學，早d練習<br />\n做mc真係唔係你想像中咁難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}